      "text": "That night, while Team Avatar was sleeping in a stone pillar field near the springs, Toph suddenly awoke when she felt vibrations in the earth warning her that someone was near. The entire gang soon woke up and saw Combustion Man standing atop the ledge that led down to the springs. A short duel was fought between the two opposing sides. Aang narrowly escaped the springs with his friends on Appa."
